                   //   How React Starts Working (Simple Steps)


//  1. Execute index.js first â€“ This is the entry point of the React application.

//  2. Fetch the root element â€“ The <div id="root"></div> is taken from index.html.

//  3. Create a React root â€“ ReactDOM.createRoot(rootElement) converts it into a React-managed root.

//  4. Render the App component â€“ The render function displays App.js inside the root.

